  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_none_summary">battery बचत गर्न system default Wi‑Fi power behavior प्रयोग गर्नुहोस्।</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_high_perf_v29_summary">screen off भएपछि voice call जस्ता अवस्थामा packet latency घटाउँछ। hardware support चाहिन्छ। Android 14 र नयाँमा यो deprecated mode low latency mode ले बदल्छ।</string>
  <string name="settings_service_wifi_lock_low_latency_summary">gaming वा virtual reality जस्ता latency-sensitive प्रयोगका लागि optimize गर्छ। battery life, throughput, Wi‑Fi scan frequency, roaming quality र location accuracy घट्न सक्छ। hardware support र screen on हुँदा यो app foreground मा running हुनुपर्छ।</string>
